  label: "AI Safety and Alignment Research",
  summary: "AI safety and alignment research is a combined field dedicated to ensuring that advanced AI systems are developed and deployed safely and in line with human values. \'Safety\' focuses on preventing harmful outcomes, while \'alignment\' specifically addresses the challenge of making AI\'s goals and behaviors match human intentions. This research explores technical solutions to prevent AI from causing unintended harm, becoming uncontrollable, or developing misaligned objectives. In AI policy, this area is crucial for guiding funding priorities, establishing ethical guidelines, and informing regulatory efforts to mitigate long-term risks from powerful AI.",
