  summary: "Dialogue systems research focuses on creating computer systems that can interact with humans using natural language, understanding and generating speech or text in a conversational manner. This field is fundamental to developing chatbots, virtual assistants, and conversational AI. In AI policy, it\'s relevant for discussions around the ethical design of AI interfaces, user experience, transparency about AI interaction, and preventing manipulation or misinformation through conversational agents.",
