  summary: "This theoretical body of work attempts to understand the nature, causes, and potential solutions for threats that could lead to human extinction or the permanent collapse of civilization. In AI policy, it provides the conceptual tools to analyze how advanced AI could pose such threats, whether through loss of control, misuse, or unintended consequences, guiding research into AI safety, alignment, and robust governance mechanisms.",
