  summary: "Fully Automated Luxury Communism is a speculative socio-economic vision where advanced automation and AI eliminate the need for human labor. This leads to an abundance of goods and services, distributed equitably, freeing humanity for leisure and creative pursuits. In AI policy, this concept frames debates about AI\'s potential to transform society, raising questions about universal basic income, wealth redistribution, and the future of work in an AI-driven economy.",
